    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute gem of a car, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream! It's been pampered since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014completely spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and has been loved so much, but it's time for a new home. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2009 Porsche 911 Carrera (997.2). This specimen features the highly-coveted 9A1 power plant with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), ensuring superior thermal management and eliminating IMS concerns. The drivetrain is paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, exhibiting perfect synchro-mesh engagement and zero clutch slippage. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), the chassis maintains original factory-spec kinematics and bushing compliance. The undercarriage is pristine, showing no signs of oxidation or fluid weepage at the rear main seal or valve covers. Finished with original factory paint depth and featuring ventilated rotors with negligible swept-area wear, this naturally aspirated flat-six is a benchmark for mechanical integrity and performance consistency.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Mint condition. Original paint. Flawless interior. No mechanical issues. Clean title.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
