    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner. This car is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it feels and smells just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, always kept it tucked away in the garage, and it drives like an absolute dream. You really won't find a cleaner ride out there. Come see it for yourself, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
